<body>
    <h1>P21 Lower Env Refresh</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h4 id=3D"P21LowerEnvRefresh-Thisdocumentdescribesthestepsfollowedt=
orefreshalowerP21Env.">
<style>[data-colorid=3Ddwx3mx8m3n]{color:#bf2600} html[data-color-mode=3Dda=
rk] [data-colorid=3Ddwx3mx8m3n]{color:#ff6640}[data-colorid=3Dito9dyy1nr]{c=
olor:#bf2600} html[data-color-mode=3Ddark] [data-colorid=3Dito9dyy1nr]{colo=
r:#ff6640}</style> This document describes the steps followed to refresh a =
lower P21 Env.</h4>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-inf=
ormation">
<span class=3D"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-informa=
tion-macro-icon"></span>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro-body">
<p>Requires elevated rights to the SQL Server.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class=3D"panel" style=3D"background-color: #FFBDAD;border-width: 1px;"=
>
<div class=3D"panelContent" style=3D"background-color: #FFBDAD;">
<p><strong>Warning:</strong> Prior to refreshing the database in P21, pleas=
e perform a check for the following items that may exist only in the lower =
environment:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Users - select * from users where delete_flag =3D 'N'</p></li>
<li>
<p>Alerts - select * from alert_implementation where row_status_flag !=3D 7=
05</p></li>
<li>
<p>Custom APIs - Found on the webserver -custom API folder</p></li>
<li>
<p>Dynachanges - select * from custom_objects where date_created &gt; =E2=
=80=9Clast refresh date=E2=80=9D</p></li>
<li>
<p>User-defined columns - select * from custom_objects_detail where date_cr=
eated &gt; 'last refresh date' and attribute_name =3D 'create'</p></li>
<li>
<p>Crystal reports - compare files in folder: db name CrystalReports</p></l=
i>
<li>
<p>Import settings - none at this time</p></li>
<li>
<p>Schedules - none at this time</p></li>
<li>
<p>Portals - compare files in folder: db name Portals</p></li>
<li>
<p>Business Rules - compare files in folder: db name BusinessRulesDLL</p></=
li>
</ul>
<p>Be sure to have a backup plan for these items before the refresh and a p=
lan to restore them afterward.</p>
</div>
</div>
<p><span style=3D"background-color: rgb(254,222,200);">If the database is P=
21Play, create a Comparato ticket to inform them that the test database wil=
l be offline. Notify Comparato when the database is back online. After the =
refresh, open a ticket with EpicCare to reconnect the B2B seller to P21Play=
.</span></p>
<p>IF P21 DEV ensure <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"http://webapps.alls=
urfaces.com:8010/CommissionClass/Assignments" rel=3D"nofollow">webapps.alls=
urfaces.com:8010/CommissionClass/Assignments</a> is working prior &amp; aft=
er refresh</p>
<h2 id=3D"P21LowerEnvRefresh-Instructions"><img class=3D"emoticon emoticon-=
blue-star" data-emoji-id=3D"1f4d8" data-emoji-shortname=3D":blue_book:" dat=
a-emoji-fallback=3D"\uD83D\uDCD8" src=3D"9d7ede15fa58aafa84c891508f1a3d4233=
cb84dd064d1cc478091d9f685da8b2" width=3D"16" height=3D"16" data-emoticon-na=
me=3D"blue-star" alt=3D"(blue star)">&nbsp;Instructions</h2>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Using Windows Explorer, copy the latest lower environment backup file fr=
om <code>\\10.0.1.72\asp21db1-dev\ASP21DB1-DEV\=E2=80=9CDB Name=E2=80=9D\FU=
LL</code> to the <code>\\10.0.1.72\BusApps_Backups</code> folder.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Rename the file to <code>=E2=80=9CDB NAME=E2=80=9DB4RefreshyyyyMMdd. Exa=
mple: P21PlayB4Refresh20250724.bak</code>.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Take the Lower Environment database offline by right-clicking on the dat=
abase and selecting "Take Offline" under Tasks. This will ensure no process=
es interfere with the restore</p><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wr=
apper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"c=
onfluence-embedded-image image-center" alt=3D"image-20250303-191433.png" wi=
dth=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"c191738ad7ae488932cac9a086e6053ccd38f05=
