109643" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"att=
achment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image-20250303-194137.png" d=
ata-base-url=3D"https://allsurfaces.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resourc=
e-content-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"373063696=
" data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"18" data-media-id=3D"7e31dcf3-a=
771-498d-b418-17315e4bd2a1" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"225"></span>=
</li>
<li>
<p>As of March 2025, the restore will take approximately 25 minutes. After =
the database restore is completed, execute the Update SQL script for that d=
atabase. The scripts are saved in the <code>Bus-Apps\Scripts &amp; Template=
s\Sanitation Scripts</code> folder.</p></li>
<li>
<p>If necessary, copy the files from following Prod folders to the refreshe=
d database folders:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>BusinessRulesDistribution</p></li>
<li>
<p>BusinessRulesDLL</p></li>
<li>
<p>CrystalReports</p></li>
<li>
<p>Logos</p></li>
<li>
<p>Portals</p></li>
<li>
<p>Middleware Custom API folder</p></li>
</ol></li>
<li>
<p>Verify the lower environment was updated correctly on both desktop and w=
eb client.</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Login into Lower Environment and verify data matches the date of P21Prod=
</p></li>
<li>
<p>Company name contains lower Environment in the description.</p></li>
<li>
<p>For P21 Dev verify is working Dev -Sales Rep to Customer.</p></li>
<li>
<p>For P21 Play the test EDI import are correct.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Spot check correct users are enabled or disabled.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Verify a form will print.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Verify a Portal is working.</p></li>
<li>
<p>If necessary, verify P21 Alerts are working</p></li>
</ol></li>
</ol>
<p></p>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-inf=
ormation">
<span class=3D"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-informa=
tion-macro-icon"></span>
